  "description": "<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201312/73ecc6ce51b84006837a28dec115deda.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t时间已经来到了2013年的岁末，离2014年的考研考试也是更近了一步，不知道考生们对于考研英语作文的准备，做得如何了？不妨一起来看下2014考研英语作文预测吧！</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>Topic：persistence/ perseverance 坚持的意义</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tThe cartoon aims at informing us of the significance of persistence. Definitely, no once can deny the importance of it. Persistence can help us carve out a way to success. Although the way to success is bumpy and filled with inevitable setbacks, it is persistence that lead us to the destination we are eager to reach. To further demonstrate the importance of being persistent， I would like to take Thomas Edison as a case in point: how could he, one of the greatest inventor throughout the history of mankind who experienced numerous unsuccessful attempts, invent the first electric lamp without persistence?</p>\n<p>\n\tAccordingly, at no time should we overlook the importance of persistence. when coming across hardships and setbacks , we need to grit our teeth and adhere to the faith that our efforts and persistence will be paid off. &ldquo;Great works are performed not by strength, but by perseverance.&rdquo; Samuel Johnson once said.</p>\n<p>\n\t<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p552561/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: #f00;\"><strong>2014考研英语作文预测汇总文&gt;&gt;</strong></span></a></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p552526/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p552526\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p553919/\">中国人全球最勤奋 网友吐槽生活所迫</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p553998/\">美国经济学教授改教韩剧 对经济绝望了！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p553051/\">2013年12月英语六级真题及答案汇总</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p551558/\">英语四六级考完做什么？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p553607/\">梳理你的人生：生活中你到底想要什么？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p103560/\">沪江英语资料下载帮助及沪元知识</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p552627/\">美国好老公：穿芭蕾裙逗乐患癌妻子</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p552519/\">天差地别：男人和女人眼里的完美美女</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p553082/\">2013年12月英语六级阅读答案及点评选词填空部分（沪江网校版）</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p554005/\">奥斯卡影后琼&bull;芳登辞世 享年96岁</a></li></ul><div style=\"margin-top: 10px;\">导航:  <a href=\"http://www.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江网</a>  <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江英语</a>  <a href=\"http://jp.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江日语</a>  <a href=\"http://fr.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江法语</a>  <a href=\"http://kr.hujiang.com\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江韩语</a></div><hr style=\"border: 0.5px solid gray;\" />", 
